Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Interface LitmusPPCVisitor<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
All Known Implementing Classes:
LitmusPPCBaseVisitor
public interface LitmusPPCVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by LitmusPPCParser.
